  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Wednesday 28th September 2016, Godalming- Surrey-</strong> Christmas is fast approaching and here at Inghams we are in full ski season spirit. As the temperatures fall in the UK and in the Alps, our chalet staff preparing to take up their winter roles and ski shops across the Alps wax skis in anticipation for the first guests. Here’s a roundup of our top 5 news items in October.</p>
<p><br />1. <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/win-a-ski-new-years-eve-holiday"><strong>Win a holiday to Méribel</strong></a> this New Year- New Year in the Alps cannot be beaten. Ski all day, have a gala dinner at one of the many chalet or Chalet Hotels followed by dancing the night away or watching the fireworks with a chilled glass of Prosecco in hand. Enter our prize draw before 31st October to win an eight night ski holiday to Méribel staying at the <a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes">Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes</a> for 2 people with return flights from London Gatwick and resort transfers. View all our New Year holidays here!</p>
<p><br />2. <strong>New <a data-udi="umb://document/07551db53774489fbf605f9446fbfd93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07551db53774489fbf605f9446fbfd93}" title="Hotel Taj-I Mah">5* Hotel, Taj-I Mah</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a></strong>- If you enjoy luxury the new 5* Taj-I Maj hotel being built in Les Arcs which offers ski-in/ ski-out accommodation at the summit of the Cabriolet ski lift is the place to stay. 7 nights, start from £1399 in February 2017 with return flights and transfers.</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052365/france_paradiski-ski-area_les-arcs_tah-l-mah-hotel.jpg" alt="Taj I Mah Hotel Les Arcs" width="486" height="486" rel="486,486" /></p>
<p>3. <strong>New Resort <a data-udi="umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606}" title="Montgenevre">Montgenèvre</a></strong>- Between France and Italy, with extensive skiing in the Milkyway ski area, (400km) Montgenèvre is a welcome addition to the Inghams programme for Winter 2016/17. Inghams is offering two new chalets, two sets of apartments and one ski inclusive hotel with a free children’s club for those aged from 3 months to 17 years old.</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052362/france_milky-way-ski-area_montgenevre.jpg" alt="Montgenevre 486Px" width="486" height="486" /></p>
<p><br />4. <strong>The London Ski Show, Battersea Park</strong>- as always Inghams will be at London Ski and Snowboard Show, Battersea Park between Thursday 27th and Sunday 30th October 2016. There will be Inghams Ski, Lakes and Mountains and Lapland experts on hand to answer any questions and even better, some fantastic holiday deals and competitions. Come and see us on stand 617 to find out more.</p>
<p><br />5. And last but by no means least, enjoy our <strong>latest <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FVz8BlhbNvc">ski video</a></strong> and please share on social media @inghamsholidays! The video aims to showcase everything we love about ski and snowboarding holidays.</p>
